        {
            "title": "施紀賢堅守立場,曼德爾森任命醜聞籠罩工黨前景",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yztcdWicAvWjMjT_21H1Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_5_M_1440048359.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 首相<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"施紀賢\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:施紀賢;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/施紀賢\">施紀賢</a>在圍繞其任命彼得·曼德爾森為駐美大使的爭議不斷升級之際,採取了強硬立場,堅決駁回要求其辭職的呼聲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在最近的一次採訪中,施紀賢將有關潛在領導層挑戰的猜測斥為政治噪音,儘管他重申任命曼德爾森——已故醜聞纏身的金融家傑弗里·愛潑斯坦的前合夥人——是一個重大錯誤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著醜聞持續主導公眾輿論,施紀賢政府目前正艱難地試圖將焦點轉回緊迫的國內外政策問題。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>信譽受到質疑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在高級公務員發表破壞性證詞後,這場風波已經削弱了首相的信譽。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-19e4eb51-a1fc-3cf1-bb2d-b39a87fb3e35-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上週,外交部前最高官員奧利·羅賓斯在議會委員會作證時表示,他受到來自唐寧街的巨大壓力,要求加快任命進程。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">奧利的說法似乎與施紀賢早前在下議院的聲明直接矛盾,當時他堅稱\"完全沒有\"對公務員系統施加壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">施紀賢試圖將這些指令描述為標準的\"政府日常壓力\",但這一矛盾為其政治對手提供了充足的攻擊彈藥。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>政治逆風加劇</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這場風波發生在工黨的關鍵時刻,該黨目前正為下月地方選舉中的重大失利做準備。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公眾對施紀賢政府的信任度下降,他與英國公務員系統——穩定治理的基石——的關係也明顯緊張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括前幕僚長摩根·麥克斯威尼在內的更多證詞預定於下週進行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者正密切關注政治僵局是否會進一步削弱政府應對日益複雜的經濟和地緣政治局勢的能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%BD%E7%B4%80%E8%B3%A2%E5%A0%85%E5%AE%88%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E7%88%BE%E6%A3%AE%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E%E7%B1%A0%E7%BD%A9%E5%B7%A5%E9%BB%A8%E5%89%8D%E6%99%AF-094954351.html",
